{"tid":2245713,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"姊弟戀性虐案押後判刑 專家指女被告已知SM有危險 日後會先徵性伴同意","createTime":"2020-10-16T12:24:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T12:57:44.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ddfc330b1f7a33b5b67fc65d1809f7261102fb2e","tid":2245713,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:24:07.000Z","msg":"大學一級榮譽畢業、從未拍拖的單身漢，透過極速約會活動，結識年長6歲的保險女經紀，兩人旋即成為情侶，更到了談婚論嫁階段。惟女方多次虐待男友，包括以風筒熱風吹男友陰莖至起水泡，及後出手搣走陰莖上結痂皮膚，復以滾水淋向他的大腿。女方又疑嫌棄做愛太快完事，狠咬男友上半身至流血，又將他撼頭埋牆甚至鉸剪插心口等。女友早前被裁定四項蓄意傷人罪名成立。辯方今指，案情輕微有如家暴，卻已令被告喪失工作和收入，更要賣樓應付訟費。被告現已深明進行性虐戀（SM）活動前要先徵得性伴同意，望獲輕判。暫委法官張天雁押後至下月2日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n39歲女被告麥凱晴（又名麥嘉雯）繼續還柙候判。她在庭上聽取求情時一度啜泣，並拉低口罩拭淚。辯方求情指，報告內容顯示被告沒有心理或精神問題。<br />\n<br />\n心理報告提及，被告已獲告知任何形式的SM活動均屬高危行為，必先獲得性伴的同意始可進行；辯方大狀指，被告現已深明這個道理，並同意報告內容。兩份報告均沒提及被告會對自己或他人造成危險，但按被告面對的壓力問題，建議給予跟進輔導。<br />\n<br />\n大狀又指，被告原本高薪厚職，前途無限，但今年7月遭解僱，失去工作和收入，更要賣樓應付訟費和彌補收入損失；她亦因被定罪，難以再在金融或銀行業立足。事件曝光後，被告的相片出現於社交媒體，亦令她承受巨大壓力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201016/T2JBN5FKK5HC7LIVVNCBN3YYHI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201016%2FT2JBN5FKK5HC7LIVVNCBN3YYHI%2F&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU0UPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=6bd4cfee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201016%2FT2JBN5FKK5HC7LIVVNCBN3YYHI%2F&h=71454c39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201016/T2JBN5FKK5HC7LIVVNCBN3YYHI/</a>"},{"pid":"fcd7456b9a4853bfe312eb31914a0f904dfcc772","tid":2245713,"uid":156863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:26:01.000Z","msg":"連開4個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843224aa1f93a98a6f7d917fed25c7449fb2fa38","tid":2245713,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcd7456b9a4853bfe312eb31914a0f904dfcc772","tid":2245713,"uid":156863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:26:01.000Z","msg":"連開4個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:27:58.000Z","msg":"開唔到4個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d250bf209780e8216b2a4c2c46d5202f47861ca","tid":2245713,"uid":29153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:35:07.000Z","msg":"我同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5ee297134d4adee71807bd3a9e90e39413d4734","tid":2245713,"uid":76804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:36:38.000Z","msg":"保險狗抵撚死 工又無左 錢又洗曬 仲要還押<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce0c693bc49d1d1d5b2a46ff9bf072f79084c49","tid":2245713,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}